{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/awkward/awesome-netherlands-events/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"1e046593-d3df-549b-8ab6-b7bdd1a460b4","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-events-in-nl-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-events-in-nl-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome events in nl awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Events in NL <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A curated list of Awesome Events in 🇳🇱</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>This list contains awesome (tech related) events happening (and are mostly recurring) in The Netherlands like: conferences, meetups and parties 🎉</p>\n<p>Contributions welcome. Add links through pull requests or create an issue to start a discussion.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\">What is an awesome list?</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">164.9k</span></span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/awkward/awesome-netherlands-events/blob/master/contributing.md\">Contribution guide</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>Want to see more awesomeness? <a href=\"https://twitter.com/madeawkward\">Follow us on Twitter</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#rotterdam\">Rotterdam</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#amsterdam\">Amsterdam</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#utrecht\">Utrecht</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#everywhere\">Everywhere</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#other\">Other</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"rotterdam\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#rotterdam\" aria-label=\"rotterdam permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Rotterdam</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://makersclubrdam.com/\">Makersclub</a> - Bimonthly casual drinkup without an agenda.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://euruko2018.org/\">EuRuKo</a> - An annual European conference about Ruby (2019).</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/nodeschool-rotterdam/\">NodeSchool</a> - Monthly meetup about learning Node.js.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://rdamsenieuwe.nl/thema/crowd-force\">Crowdsource</a> - Crowdsource ideas for startups.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"amsterdam\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#amsterdam\" aria-label=\"amsterdam permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Amsterdam</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://makersclubams.com/\">Makersclub</a> - Bimonthly casual drinkup without an agenda.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Hackers-and-Founders-Amsterdam-NL/\">Hackers &#x26; Founders</a> - Monthly meetup at Cafe De Doffer.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thenextweb.com/conference\">The Next Web Conference</a> - Biggest tech conference (May 18 &#x26; 19).</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://amsxtech.com/\">AMSxTech</a> - Community driven conference (March 31) and monthly meetups.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://functionconf.io/\">FunctionConf</a> - Conference about serverless architectures (June 15 &#x26; 16).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/amsterdam-rb/\">Amsterdam-rb</a> - Active Ruby meetup with frequent, large events.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Amsterdam-Elixir\">Amsterdam-Elixir</a> - Monthly Elixir meetups.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Rust-Amsterdam\">Amsterdam-Rust</a> - Monthly meetups and workshops around Rust.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Lead-Developers-Amsterdam\">Lead Developers Amsterdam</a> - For Lead Developers, Tech Leads, Chapter Leads and Senior Engineers heading towards Lead positions.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.devopsdays.org/events/2019-amsterdam/welcome/\">DevOps Day Amsterdam</a> - Development, operations, QA, InfoSec, management, and leadership.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://react.amsterdam\">React Amsterdam</a> - React Amsterdam is a <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/React-Amsterdam/\">Meetup group</a> and a full day conference (April 21) on all things React.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://webcrafters.xyz\">Webcrafters</a> - Biweekly meetup where you can work on your sideproject.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"utrecht\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#utrecht\" aria-label=\"utrecht permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Utrecht</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.thekick030.nl\">The Kick 030</a> - Two monthly event with talks about the creative industry.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://creativeshowoff.nl\">Creative Show-off</a> - Pitch your idea/business while drinking a beer.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"everywhere\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#everywhere\" aria-label=\"everywhere permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Everywhere</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/CocoaHeadsNL/\">CocoaHeads</a> - Monthly meetup about iOS and MacOS development.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://coderdojo.nl\">CoderDojo</a> - Monthly workshops for kids (7-17) to learn to code.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.designbyfire.nl\">Design by Fire Café</a> - Conferences and Gatherings on Interaction Design.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"other\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#other\" aria-label=\"other permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Other</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://lanyrd.com/places/netherlands/\">Lanyrd</a> - Directory of conferences and events.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/find/?allMeetups=false&#x26;keywords=tech&#x26;radius=100&#x26;userFreeform=netherlands&#x26;gcResults=Netherlands%3ANL%3Anull%3Anull%3Anull%3Anull%3Anull%3A52.132633%3A5.2912659999999505&#x26;change=yes&#x26;sort=member_count\">Meetup</a> - Directory of meetups.</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#awesome-events-in-nl-awesome\">Awesome Events in NL <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#c